Hi, I'm Khawar. I'm a developer from Azad Kashmir, Pakistan.

Most of my work is web and backend. I work with the PHP, Laravel, 
FilamentPHP, WordPress and MERN stack.

I like open source. A lot of what I know came from other people's
code that they put out for free, so I try to give back what I can.
If something I made saves you some time, that's the whole point.

